mixin popup()
    .popup#callback 
        button(type='button').popup-close.popup__overlay
        .popup__body
            button(type='button').popup-close.popup__close 
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M9.16998 14.83L14.83 9.16998" stroke="#1F1F1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <path d="M14.83 14.83L9.16998 9.16998" stroke="#1F1F1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <path d="M9 22H15C20 22 22 20 22 15V9C22 4 20 2 15 2H9C4 2 2 4 2 9V15C2 20 4 22 9 22Z" stroke="#1F1F1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
            p.popup__title Записаться на #[span бесплатное] пробное занятие
            form(action="#!").form__content 
                input(type="text" placeholder="Ваше имя").form__input.input.popup__input 
                input(type="text" placeholder="Ваш телефон").form__input.input.popup__input 
                button(type="submit").form__btn.btn.popup__btn Записаться
                p.form__p Отправляя заявку вы соглашаетесь#[br]с #[a(href="privacy.html") политикой конфиденциальности]
    .popup#thanks 
        button(type='button').popup-close.popup__overlay
        .popup__body
            button(type='button').popup-close.popup__close 
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M9.16998 14.83L14.83 9.16998" stroke="#1F1F1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <path d="M14.83 14.83L9.16998 9.16998" stroke="#1F1F1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <path d="M9 22H15C20 22 22 20 22 15V9C22 4 20 2 15 2H9C4 2 2 4 2 9V15C2 20 4 22 9 22Z" stroke="#1F1F1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
            p.thanks-title Спасибо за вашу заявку!
            p.thanks-p Наш специалист скоро свяжется с вами
            